"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-15-nnpp-chieftain-decries-nigerias-performance-at-paris-olympic\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published on By A chieftain of the New Nigeria People's Party, NNPP, Olufemi Ajadi Oguntoyinbo has described the over N12bn spent at the 2024 Paris Olympics competition as a 'wastage'.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A chieftain\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 27}, {\"ngram\": \"the New Nigeria People's Party\", \"from\": 31, \"to\": 61}, {\"ngram\": \"NNPP\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 67}, {\"ngram\": \"Olufemi Ajadi Oguntoyinbo\", \"from\": 69, \"to\": 94}, {\"ngram\": \"N12bn\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 123}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics competition\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 168}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'wastage\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He decried the failure of Nigeria's contingent at the just concluded games and their failure to clinch any medals despite the huge financial commitment by the government.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2446460124112526e-18, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the failure\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 211}, {\"ngram\": \"the just concluded games\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"their failure\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"any medals\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 302}, {\"ngram\": \"the huge financial commitment\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 340}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DAILY POST gathered that Nigeria fielded 88 athletes in 12 sports in Paris and ended up without a medal.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5663276047428435e-14, \"text\": \"DAILY POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2446460124112526e-18, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999394174215669, \"rank\": 6.058624890663427e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"88 athletes\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"12 sports\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The NNPP chieftain in his reaction, said the amount that was invested is painful because there were no results to show for it.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The NNPP chieftain\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"his reaction\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"no results\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added that it is almost two times the amount of the country's entire budget for the Ministry of Science and Technology this year.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"almost two times the amount\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's entire budget\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ministry\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"Science\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"Technology\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oguntoyinbo in a statement made available to DAILY POST on Thursday, then called on the Federal government to probe the cause of this wastage and failure.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5663276047428435e-14, \"text\": \"DAILY POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oguntoyinbo\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"the Federal government\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the cause\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"this wastage\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"failure\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He urged the Federal government to focus more on Science and Technology development as they are doing on sports.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Federal government\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"Science and Technology development\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The NNPP chieftain said, \\\"We fielded 88 athletes in 12 sports with 12bn in Paris and ended up without a medal, this is over N136 million (about $85,000) spent on each of the 88 Nigerian contingents to the Olympics, and no singular medal was won.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999394174215669, \"rank\": 6.058624890663427e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.981329326245497, \"rank\": 0.019025900128781012, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The NNPP chieftain\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"88 athletes\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"12 sports\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"12bn\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"no singular medal\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While Jamaica, a nation which spent far less than we did, a total of about $2300 on each contingent, won 6 medals; 1 Gold, 3 Silver and 2 Bronze at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999844706488429, \"rank\": 1.509123676951854e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nation\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"each contingent\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"6 medals\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"3 Silver\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"2 Bronze\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We must now question how we made this huge investment, without getting any returns.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this huge investment\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"any returns\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now that the Paris Olympics 2024 has officially ended and Team Nigeria, despite the huge financial investment made into the project, returned without a single medal amounts to wastage.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2446460124112526e-18, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"the huge financial investment\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"a single medal\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"wastage\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let me call on the Federal Government to institute a probe into the performance of our 88 contingent to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.5566622663148296, \"rank\": 0.7905638863514632, \"text\": \"Federal Government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a probe\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"our 88 contingent\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to register my displeasure with the recklessness and shoddy preparation for the Olympics leading to a wastage of over N12bn.\"